  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA18">
<l>tāmpālāp puṇṭālu mattaḻumpu tāṉiḷaka</l>
<l>pāmpālāp puṇṭupā ṭuṟṟāluñ cōmpātip</l>
<l>palluruvai yellām paṭarvitta vittāvuṉ</l>
<l>ṟolluruvai yāraṟivār collu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O knowing one who set forth all these many forms, not idle,</l>
<l>as soon as he was involved in the snake’s being bound</l>
<l>so that that scar faded [that he had received] as soon as he had been bound,</l>
<l>who knows your old form, speak?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
